      <item>
        <title>Stop Wishing, Start Doing: Stoic Quotes to Ignite Action and Focus</title>
        <link>https://wirtaw.github.io/blog/en/blog/stop-wishing-start-doing-stoic/</link>
        <description>&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You don&#39;t need more time, you need less distractions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You don&#39;t need motivation, you need self-control.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You don&#39;t need more resources, you need resourcefulness.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You don&#39;t need luck, you need preparation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You don&#39;t need to be busy, you need to be focused.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You don&#39;t need to know everything, you just need to start.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You have everything you need.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
